ADDITIONAL NOTICES:

This software uses MANO hand models which are subject to separate licensing terms.
MANO models must be obtained from https://mano.is.tue.mpg.de/ and are provided
for research purposes only. Users must agree to MANO's license terms separately.

This software uses MediaPipe Hands for hand landmark detection.
MediaPipe is licensed under Apache License 2.0.
See: https://github.com/google/mediapipe

This software uses the FreiHAND dataset for training and evaluation.
FreiHAND is provided for research purposes only. Commercial use is prohibited.
Users must cite the FreiHAND paper when using this dataset:
  @InProceedings{Freihand2019,
    author    = {Christian Zimmermann, Duygu Ceylan, Jimei Yang, Bryan Russell, Max Argus and Thomas Brox},
    title     = {FreiHAND: A Dataset for Markerless Capture of Hand Pose and Shape from Single RGB Images},
    booktitle = {IEEE International Conference on Computer Vision (ICCV)},
    year      = {2019},
    url       = {https://lmb.informatik.uni-freiburg.de/projects/freihand/}
  }
See: https://lmb.informatik.uni-freiburg.de/resources/datasets/FreiHand.en.html
